---
import { images } from "../data/images";
---

<section class="about tint" id="about">
  <div class="sec-label reveal" style="grid-column: 1 / -1">
    <span class="num">04 / Studio</span>
    <h2>A quiet room<br>for <em>unquiet</em> bodies.</h2>
  </div>

  <p class="about-lede reveal">
    We believe the hour you give us should be the
    <em>best hour</em> of your day. Unhurried, precise, and honest
    about what your body actually needs.
  </p>

  <div class="about-body reveal">
    <p class="small">Founded 2022</p>
    <p>
      Studio 17 is Emma's studio. She opened it after a decade between
      London rehabilitation clinics and a classical studio in Manchester.
      With one idea: a reformer room where no one is ever left in the back row.
    </p>
    <p>
      Every class is taught by Emma. There is no rotating roster, no
      substitute to get used to. She'll remember where you were last
      week and meet you where you are this one.
    </p>
    <p>
      New here? Begin with a <a href="/bookings" style="text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 4px;">Studio Intro</a>, a 60 minute
      private to meet the equipment, your teacher, and your starting line.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="principles reveal">
    <div>
      <div class="k">Teacher</div>
      <div class="v">One, <em>always</em>. Emma.</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="k">Equipment</div>
      <div class="v">Gratz &amp; <em>Balanced Body</em></div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="k">Class size</div>
      <div class="v">Never more than <em>six</em></div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="k">Pace</div>
      <div class="v">Deliberate, <em>slow</em>, strong</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-photo reveal">
    <div class="ph">
      <img src={images.studioInterior} alt="Studio 17 interior, reformers and natural light" />
      <span class="ph-label"><span class="sq"></span> Studio interior · wide</span>
      <span class="ph-tag">IMG · 02 · 16 : 7</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
